        <h2 id="visit-title">A Google Maps embed makes the demo feel placed in the world.</h2>
        <p>The demo uses a real Google Maps embed for a deliberately fictional lunch-club pin borrowed from the New York Stock Exchange area. Ordering, delivery, bookings, payments, and live location management remain add-ons.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Garden steps and tables shown in the hero photo.</li>
          <li>Counter pickup before patio seating.</li>
          <li>Static directions repeated in text for accessibility.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <figure class="map-card table-scene">
