        </details>
        <figcaption>Google Maps screenshot plus optional live iframe · fictional demo location</figcaption>
        <p class="map-fallback"><strong>Static directions:</strong> Walk toward the garden steps, find the green counter, then check the board before taking a table.</p>
      </figure>
